          <h4 class="title">Refund Policy</h4>
          <p>At Harisree Handlooms, we value your satisfaction. If you're not completely happy with your purchase, we’re here to help with an easy and transparent refund process.</p>

          <h4 class="title">Eligibility for Refunds</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Refunds are only applicable to products that are damaged, defective, or incorrectly delivered.</li>
            <li>The item must be unused, in its original packaging, and accompanied by a valid proof of purchase.</li>
            <li>Refund requests must be submitted within <strong>7 days</strong> from the date of delivery.</li>
          </ul>

          <h4 class="title">Non-refundable Items</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Products that have been used, washed, or damaged due to customer handling.</li>
            <li>Items bought during a clearance sale or using promotional discounts unless found defective.</li>
            <li>Customized or tailored handloom products.</li>
          </ul>

          <h4 class="title">Refund Process</h4>
          <p>Once your return is received and inspected, we will notify you via email or phone about the status of your refund.</p>
          <p>If approved, the refund will be processed to your original payment method within <strong>7 working days</strong>.</p>

          <h4 class="title">Shipping Charges</h4>
          <p>Shipping charges are non-refundable. The cost of return shipping will be borne by the customer unless the product is found to be faulty or damaged.</p>

          <h4 class="title">How to Request a Refund</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Email us at <a href="mailto:harisreehandlooms@gmail.com">harisreehandlooms@gmail.com</a> with your order ID, reason for refund, and pictures (if applicable).</li>
            <li>Our support team will get back to you within 24–48 hours with further instructions.</li>
          </ul>

          <h4 class="title">Contact Us</h4>
          <p>If you have any questions or need help regarding your refund, feel free to reach out to us at <a href="mailto:harisreehandlooms@gmail.com">harisreehandlooms@gmail.com</a>.</p>

          <h4 class="title">Policy Updates</h4>
          <p>Harisree Handlooms reserves the right to modify or update this refund policy at any time without prior notice. Please check this page periodically for any changes.</p>

        </div>
